{"type": "article", "id": 30801, "title": "智能吐司机", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608092044339W6OQxpJZ2UDLbgi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>想在吐司上煎出漂亮的图案或者是一句暖心的留言却不知道如何下手？这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.toasteroid.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Toasteroid</a> 的机器可以帮你做出一份充满趣味的吐司，它有一个配套的应用，下载后通过蓝牙向机器传输数据。只要在手机上进行简单的操作，吐司就会煎出订制的图案或者留言，颜色的深浅也可以自由控制。除此之外，你还可以选择在吐司上煎出当日的天气和温度，让本来单调的早餐时间变得更加有趣。你这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/258723592/toasteroid-first-app-controlled-smart-image-toaste\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809204453lbicsgG1VUEOrIWT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809204454kF2uEKwzBgHfjvVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.069444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809204454dZRzFSOhrk91YAux.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.233824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}